# invalid-escape-single-quote

## Input

```
a 'bad\z'

```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..10
  ENTRY@0..10
    WORD_KEY@0..1
      WORD@0..1 "a"
    SPACE@1..2 " "
    QUOTED_STRING@2..9
      SINGLE_QUOTE@2..3 "'"
      STRING@3..8 "bad\\z"
      SINGLE_QUOTE@8..9 "'"
    NEWLINE@9..10 "\n"
```

## AST

```
SourceFile {
    shebang: none,
    items: [
        Entry {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@0..1 "a",
            },
            value: QuotedString {
                open_quote: SINGLE_QUOTE@2..3 "'",
                string: STRING@3..8 "bad\\z",
                close_quote: SINGLE_QUOTE@2..3 "'",
            },
        },
    ],
}
```

